high_descs: step to the stove and turn to the right and take a few steps and turn to the left and take a step and turn to the right and go to the small table
take the green sponge from the table
turn to the left twice and take a few steps  and turn to the right facing the white table
put the sponge in the pan on the table
pick up the pan with the sponge in it from the table
turn to the right twice and take a few steps and turn to the left and go to the counter top
put the pan with the sponge in it on the counter top left of the sink
anns.task_desc: Place a pan with the sponge in it on the sink counter top

high_descs: Turn right and cross the room to the black shelves at the left of the sink cabinet.
Get the green sponge from the back of the top shelf.
Turn around the other direction and go to the frying pan on the table with the toaster on it.
Put the sponge in the frying pan.
Pick up the frying pan with the sponge in it.
Carry the frying pan with the sponge in it to the sink cabinet on your right and face the counter on the left side of the sink.
Set the frying pan holding the sponge on the counter to the left of the knife, leaving it with the handle pointing toward you.
anns.task_desc: Put a frying pan with a sponge in it on a counter by the kitchen sink.

high_descs: Walk forward to the store, turn right, and walk forward to the counter.
Pick up the sponge behind the tomato
Turn around, walk forward a couple steps, then turn right to face the table.
Place the sponge in the frying pan
Pick up the frying pan
Turn around, walk forward a step, then turn left and walk until you hit the counter
Place the frying pan onto the counter, to the left of the fork and knife
anns.task_desc: Move the frying pan to the counter, with the sponge in it.
